Package: LStest
Type: Package
Title: Makes DfT Excel tables (based off "xltabr" MoJ package)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Luke", "Shaw", email = "Luke.Shaw@dft.gsi.gov.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Luke Shaw <Luke.Shaw@dft.gsi.gov.uk>
Description: This package makes it possible to import data from an API and
    manipulate it into the format of the desired Excel table, then using
    DfT styles can output the table in a consistent, user-friendly format
    as a .xlsx file suitable for publication.
